Shareterm allows you to easily share a terminal on UNIX systems over a network.
It require a central server with SSH accounts for each people wanting to use the
system.

DEPENDS (client side)
---------------------
python python-paramiko screen openssh-server sudo fluxbox vncserver xvncviewer
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|> Recommanded install command under Ubuntu / Debian :
|   apt-get install python python-paramiko openssh-server screen tightvncserver xtightvncviewer fluxbox
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

(server side)
-------------
python sudo openssh-server
